.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
City: berlin, hamburg, edinburgh, prague
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
House: victorian, tower, townhouse, gothic-revival
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the townhouse house##1
10. the victorian house is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| City      | hamburg      | berlin     | edinburgh    | prague |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| House   | tower  | gothic-revival     | townhouse    | victorian         |
| Pet           | rat         | hamster | pony     | ferret        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

