.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, tulip, amaryllis, rose
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapefruit, pepper, raspberry
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, japanese, thai
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, guinea-pig, snake
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, january, may
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Flower      | amaryllis   | rose   | tulip      | iris     |
| Food          | pepper     | garlic   | raspberry | grapefruit |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | chinese   | thai       |
| Pet           | goat       | cat      | snake     | guinea-pig |
| Birthday     | june    | january     | may     | november     |

