 8. the person traveling to nizza is the dancer##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

